entries.femaleVariant: All right. We don't got the scratch, there's still another way.
Gotta go down by the Totentanz. Heard they're 'bout to toss some fresh samples on the street.
Fuck, man! You gonked? You even know how many good chooms we lost to that shit?
Dunno what Maelstrom cuts in their stuff, but it ain't baby powder. More like rat poison.
Or... maybe it's just that good?
Good stuff shouldn't leave you face down in your own puke.
Risk's part of the game, choom. You know that.
Fine! Go shoot your gonk self in the head. That shit's risky, too.
